text: Kałmy is a settlement in Gmina, Korsze, in Kętrzyn County in Poland. It is around 1 mile north east of Korsze, 12 miles north west of Kętrzyn and 39 miles north east of the closest city Olsztyn. == References == Category:Settlements in Poland Category:Warmian-Masurian Voivodeship
title: Kałmy
